	f age. No babies in arms. There is no elevator. Stairs only to the balcony
	 level.\nMetal detectors & bag search at door. Arrive early. No weapons. w
	ww.stgpresents.org/about/safety When purchasing ADA accessible seating\, p
	lease feel free to contact us by email if assistance is needed with accomm
	odations or companion seating\; you may reach us at accessibility@stgprese
	nts.org. Each accessible seat houses an armless freestanding chair for pat
